{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 87.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, then I looked down the street and I saw the main gate, I decided I would not go in that way because if they were going to defend it, that would be the most likely place to defend.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had the company deploy off to the left of the gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, at that time, then we ran into a railway [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] train that had 39 cars in it, various types of boxcars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of-- some of them were old passenger cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some were open, gondola type, like coal cars, or [? over ?] cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then there was a spur line leading from Dachau, the city of Dachau, into the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- on that train, there were-- each car was filled with human bodies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were all dead, as far as we could determine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, we searched through the-- these-- about 40 cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as-- all we found was dead, dead people in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Obviously civilians-- that they had on-- well, they had-- some of them had on striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had on miscellaneous clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some had had enough strength to crawl out and have-- fell on the ground near the railway car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were about 2,000 dead in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, my men-- there was a lot of-- much, much said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I could see the men were getting very angry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then I gave the order, well, let's, let's go into the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you know what was-- who these civilians were that were dead?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have any idea where they came from, or what they were doing there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As all we knew is we found a railway car with-- as I recall, there were 39 cars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each was filled with dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
